Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好好好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲刺冲刺！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.63,0:00:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗准备！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手的眼睛很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在把他们引至一击必杀范围内之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让他们发现我们的武装
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能只有那么小一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东条 其余的敌人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌1的后方三公里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以每小时200公里速度接近的敌2 一分钟就到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑错对手算你们倒霉！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停船！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停船就不杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要停啊 笨蛋！

